cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "MLLM: Ontology-Constrained Multi-LLM Evidence-Mapping Pipeline"
abstract: "Public implementation scaffold for ontology-constrained literature synthesis using local large language model councils, HPC-36 predictive-coding factors, local/global oddball scoring, and auditable model-derived evidence annotations."
